Description: Fix CVE-2026-50256: font alias stack-based buffer overflow (ZDI-CAN-30136)
 The X server's 256-byte stack buffer for font alias resolution
 (XLFDMAXFONTNAMELEN) is undersized relative to libXfont2's 1024-byte
 alias target name length (MAXFONTNAMELEN).  Alias names of 257-1023
 bytes overflow the stack buffer used in dixfonts.c's font alias lookup
 path, leading to a crash or potential privilege escalation when the X
 server runs as root.
 .
